name: thepiratebay.org - dark blue redesign
description:
Complete redesign of thepiratebay.org with the same colors etc as style 844 and my style style 1824. All ads are removed as well.

NOTICE:

The Piratebay logo on the frontpage was too big to be added into the style (userstyles.org only allows 65k characters) so i added the logo as before picture. Enter it as data:uri where i marked it in the code.
